                                                     <span id="dgPanelHistory_ctl02_Label1"><b>05 Dec 2007</b></span>
                                                </td><td align="left" valign="middle" width="70%">
																	
																	<span id="dgPanelHistory_ctl02_Label1"><b>Engineering Socio-Technical Systems Panel</b></span>
